## Group Listing

### Listing [GET /listing{?alcoholType}]

Returns a listing for each type of alcoholic beverage in the inventory.

+ Parameters
    + alcoholType: beer (enum[string], optional) - The type of alcohol to list.
        + Members
            + beer
            + spirit
            + wine
    
+ Response 200 (application/json;charset=UTF-8)

    Listing of alcoholic beverages.
    
    + Attributes
        :[](common/status.apib)
        + result (object, required)
            :[](resources/listing.apib)
            
## Group Serving

### Serving [GET /serving{?id}]

Returns a serving of the specified alcoholic beverage.

+ Parameters
    + id: Hell's Pale Ale (string, required) - The specific beverage, unique identifier across all types of alcohol
    
+ Response 200 (application/json;charset=UTF-8)

    A serving.
    
    + Attributes
        :[](common/status.apib)
        + result (object, required)
            :[](resources/serving.apib)
            
+ Response 400 (application/json;charset=UTF-8)

    Invalid/missing beverage id.
    
    + Attributes
        :[](common/error_400.apib)
        
+ Response 401 (application/json;charset=UTF-8)

    No age proof provided.
    
    + Attributes
        :[](common/error_401.apib)
        
